                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p><strong><a href="/scp-series-1-tales-edition">&lt;&lt;&lt; Series 1 Tales List</a> | <a href="/scp-series-2-tales-edition">&lt; Series 2 Tales List</a> | <a href="/scp-series-3-tales-edition">&lt; Series 3 Tales List</a> | <a href="/scp-series-4-tales-edition">&lt; Series 4 Tales List</a></strong></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone series">
